                            <comment id="13941554" author="chetanm" created="Thu, 20 Mar 2014 09:37:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;As per default setting &lt;a href=&quot;http://api.mongodb.org/java/current/com/mongodb/MongoOptions.html#cursorFinalizerEnabled&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;cursors are closed on finalize&lt;/a&gt; but yes it would be better to close the cursor&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13941586" author="amitjain" created="Thu, 20 Mar 2014 10:17:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;There is a default close after 10 minutes too.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;From &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
By default, the server will automatically close the cursor after 10 minutes of inactivity or if client has exhausted the cursor&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://docs.mongodb.org/manual/core/cursors/#cursors&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://docs.mongodb.org/manual/core/cursors/#cursors&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13948505" author="mreutegg" created="Wed, 26 Mar 2014 21:33:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed in &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/r1582072&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/r1582072&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13962847" author="alex.parvulescu" created="Tue, 8 Apr 2014 12:47:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;bulk close for the 0.20.0 release&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
